  <brief_title>Tamoxifen Compared With Clomiphene Citrate for Women Who Had Thin Endometrium Women Under Clomiphene in a Previous Cycle</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Randomized Study of Ovulation Induction Using Either Tamoxifen or Clomiphene Citrate for Women Who Had Thin Endometrium During Previous Treatment With Clomiphene Citrate</official_title>
