  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Primary or secondary infertility due to:

          -  Ovulatory dysfunction

          -  Mild male infertility

          -  Unexplained infertility

          -  Endometrium &lt; 6 mm at time of hCG during previous treatment with clomiphene citrate

          -  Age 18-35

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Serious adverse effects under clomiphene citrate or known sensitivity to either
             tamoxifen or clomiphene citrate
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
